comment.author: 25053835@N03
comment._content: This photo is part of an ongoing digitization and research project at the Smithsonian Institution Archives. Please help us research Miss W. Dennis. View a related blog post here - blog.photography.si.edu/2009/03/30/who-are-you/

comment.author: 11418107@N02
comment._content: Could be Olive D. Wetzel Dennis (b. 1885), a Pennsylvania-born service engineer for the Baltimore & Ohio Railroad; she held a number of patents, an MA in mathematics and a PhD in civil engineering.
